item.title: Need compiler
item.dc:creator: @xoskullxo13 xoskullxo13
item.description:
@xoskullxo13 wrote:

[quote=“Jordiescape, post:3, topic:231642”]@echo off title Compiling... "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java title Compiled... pause
If that doesn’t work download java here.
Or change the;

"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java

To;

"C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java

Add that to notepad, then save it as Compile.bat
Or…
copy in the above, then go to your source, then right-click on your compiler and press “edit” then press Ctrl+ A (Select All) Then press Ctrl+V (Paste)
